<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id83e81895-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s4502"><num value="4502">§ 4502.</num><heading> Payment</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id83e81896-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s4502/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Basis for Payment</inline>.—</heading><chapeau>When practicable, payments under <ref href="/us/usc/t41/s4501">section 4501 of this title</ref> shall be made on any of the following bases:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id83e81897-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s4502/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> Performance measured by objective, quantifiable methods such as delivery of acceptable items, work measurement, or statistical process controls.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id83e81898-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s4502/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> Accomplishment of events defined in the program management plan.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id83e81899-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s4502/a/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> Other quantifiable measures of results.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id83e8189a-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s4502/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Payment Amount</inline>.—</heading><content>Payments made under <ref href="/us/usc/t41/s4501">section 4501 of this title</ref> may not exceed the unpaid contract price.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id83e8189b-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/350/s3">Pub. L. 111–350, § 3</ref>, <date date="2011-01-04">Jan. 4, 2011</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3791">124 Stat. 3791</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
